A first virtual operator will win the Czech Republic this same year.
Maybe
The mobile market in Czechia is relatively advanced, and our operators offer practically the same services as their partners in Western Europe.
Nevertheless, we still lack something - a virtual operator, who would force classical operators to lower prices.
He may not be missing for a long time.
We have already mentioned, again and again, on Mobil.cz the fact that Czech operators are part of Europe's most dear ones.
